<!-- PRODUCT 01 -->
<div class="wrap"><div class="prod" style="border-top:none">
  <div class="pt">
    <span class="ey stencil">01 · The register</span>
    <h3>One register, in the open.</h3>
    <p>Milestones, the active hold, register health — read at a glance, the same truth for everyone on the programme.</p>
    <ul><li>Register health on every screen</li><li>The one active hold, where it sits</li><li>Figures feed the QPR pack directly</li></ul>
  </div>
  <div class="pg">
    <div class="pm">
